 986: **Finding 7: an audit-parameterized baseline — what it does and does not
 987: calibrate.** The manuscript-review round's sharpest attack held that the zero-control
 988: baseline is a caricature — real administrations run audit institutions,
 989: retentions, bonds, and inspection — and the answer was a seventh
